{
  "stem": "15393.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She would have to do that in order to get out of the ghetto with her group going to her work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That is not necessary anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That group either cannot get out or if they get out, they cannot come back again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew that if she wants to get back into the ghetto, she will be taken away at the gate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I decided there and then that I'm going to escape from the ghetto and try to prevent her from coming.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have to get to her in time that she does know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, that was not very easy for money, from any aspect, but certainly to begin with because I knew that I must not utter a sound about my intentions to my grandparents because they would never allow me.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They would never let me go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that was in my decision, how to do it, how to overcome all the obstacles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everybody that night was going down to the cellar, where there was a particular part of the cellar made to a hiding place, a sort of under the floor boards and so on.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was detached a little bit from the other part of the cellar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Of course, ludicrous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If they had come and wanted to find with a dog, one dog would sniff it out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But-- but one was, you know, one was so naive thinking, oh, nobody will find us here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Nonsense, they would have done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But this is where we all-- all the inhabitants of the house-- went down through these floorboards, down the ladder, into that particular hiding cellar, me-- myself included, of course.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I thought I shall wait until such a time when everybody is fast asleep and then I'll try.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
